</title>
<subSubSection id="427F9AA68F5E11E79DA682D43DFFCF89" pageId="null" pageNumber="590" type="description">
<paragraph id="012AFC3E027FCEDA59BC04ADFE2980E4" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">
Ausdauernd. Stengel verzweigt, 
<normalizedToken id="68CA6D02293253219852CCF9ED514216" originalValue="beblättert" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">beblaettert</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="ACCEF294DBDD8558222F4818F4BD76C5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">
<normalizedToken id="9F4413E6775E2A0A4BAEE12F046CC930" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
vor und 
<normalizedToken id="2B1721EE7352F2B913BE67D3C2F8C612" originalValue="während" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">waehrend</normalizedToken>
der 
<normalizedToken id="C235C537E6F78845BF35BEFF62BE5CEF" originalValue="Blütezeit" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Bluetezeit</normalizedToken>
nickend.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="CA4416BD005442CABBBEDFD3E1A2A80D" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Huelle</normalizedToken>
zylindrisch; 
<normalizedToken id="FDC334A16EA2957DF4E848E18A15B7B8" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
in 2 Reihen, die 
<normalizedToken id="CADFF5A8263CD12BCD25890305263C9D" originalValue="äußern" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">aeussern</normalizedToken>
viel kleiner als die innern. Boden des 
<normalizedToken id="F44318A4B180C4599BC7B30BAEC2D558" originalValue="Blütenkopfes" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Bluetenkopfes</normalizedToken>
ohne 
<normalizedToken id="1BAB0F227763EC29E8372DBD26807371" originalValue="Spreublätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Spreublaetter</normalizedToken>
, kahl. 
<emphasis id="690B4D06FDB65D819A0381E24886C474" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">
<normalizedToken id="348AD8F4324D4A22FC787E71D374CBE9" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Blueten</normalizedToken>
purpurn, violett
</emphasis>
, 
<normalizedToken id="74ACB3A73385099DC3E449100157E333" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">weiss</normalizedToken>
oder gelblich. 
<normalizedToken id="B5578E9FE5ECDA6739C2B76E431C24C8" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
zylindrisch, kantig, 
<emphasis id="87A834BAE1F22361545C9C3D1EFAE02C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">
an der Spitze kaum 
<normalizedToken id="ADB2F9ABE9F6DAABC5A288CBEBCE14A6" originalValue="verschmälert" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">verschmaelert</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="C09B7F63260ADA94FC5AE271C46E18A0" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Pappus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="590" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pappus</taxonomicName>
meist 2reihig, aus rauhen Borsten bestehend.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B2C222D5D84E59EDA9D4117997518423" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">
Die Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="5AD06BB819B371249DC5FD12A82F2CEB" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Prenanthes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="590" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="27E9ED21748391E8B103FE79326782E8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Prenanthes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="3A591F23DF141B370735F38A1C4BE44A" originalValue="umfaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">umfasst</normalizedToken>
etwa 
<emphasis id="5F72DBCFAE62C00F26B81F31D4AE905E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">40 Arten</emphasis>
, von denen die meisten in 
<emphasis id="DA8A543195944B41455514958548B8D3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Ostasien und Nordamerika</emphasis>
Vorkommen. In 
<taxonomicName id="7829843DAC9966FEAF77FFE7BDD0D137" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Europa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="590" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Europa</taxonomicName>
ist nur 1 Art, die eventuell weiter aufgeteilt werden kann, vorhanden. 
<emphasis id="23F666BAC56573255F063E2A9CE2A4BF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Chromosomengrundzahlen</emphasis>
n = 8 und 9.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
